                              <title type="complete" ref="LIT3985Mazmura"/>
                              <note>
                                The word እግዚአብሔር is rubricated, occasionally in alternating red and black letters. f. 50r two words "half of the Psalms" surround in line of alternating red and black dots marking the midpoint of the psalms. Psalm 118 contains the spiritual meanings of the Hebrew letters.‎7.‎	Columetric layout of text: f. 93v (Ps. 150)‎. Ff. 86rv (Ps. 135) has rubrication in last word on right margin.‎
